OL,3,CMan in court accused of causing the
OL,4,Cdeath of father and son by dangerous
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,FA man has appeared in court charged
OL,8,Fover a head-on collision that took
OL,9,Fplace over the Christmas period in
OL,10,Fwhich a father and son were killed.
OL,12,FThe court heard that the man is
OL,13,Fdiabetic and the last thing he
OL,14,Fremembers before the crash was feeling
OL,15,Fthat his blood sugar was low.
OL,17,FPeter Devlin and his son Loughlin were
OL,18,Fkilled in the two-car crash outside
OL,19,FKillylea in Co Armagh on the afternoon
OL,20,Fof December 27.
