OL,3,CMan in court accused of causing the
OL,4,Cdeath of father and son by dangerous
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,FIvan Petrov, 32, a Bulgarian national
OL,8,Fwho the court heard has been in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland since 2015 but who
OL,10,Fhas no permanent address in the
OL,11,Fjurisdiction, appeared before Newry
OL,12,FMagistrates Court on Friday.
OL,14,FHe is charged with two counts of
OL,15,Fcausing the deaths of Peter and
OL,16,FLoughlin Devlin by dangerous driving
OL,17,Fand one count of causing grievous
OL,18,Fbodily injury to Ursula Devlin by
OL,19,Fdangerous driving.
