OL,3,CMan in court accused of causing the
OL,4,Cdeath of father and son by dangerous
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,FA constable told the court that the
OL,8,Fserious collision on Killylea Road
OL,9,Ftook place at around 12.43pm last
OL,10,FFriday between an Audi and a Mercedes.
OL,12,FMr Petrov, the driver and the sole
OL,13,Foccupant of the Audi, was taken to
OL,14,Fhospital with rib and arm fractures.
OL,16,FLoughlin Devlin, who was driving the
OL,17,FMercedes, and his father Peter Devlin,
OL,18,Fwho was a rear-seat passenger, died at
OL,19,Fthe scene of the crash.
