OL,7,FThe constable told the court that
OL,8,Ffollowing a forensic examination of
OL,9,Fthe scene, it is believed that the
OL,10,Fhead-on collision took place in the
OL,11,FMercedes' lane and that they believe
OL,12,Fthe Audi entered the wrong side of the
OL,13,Froad.
OL,15,FThe court heard that witnesses also
OL,16,Freported that the Audi had travelled
OL,17,Finto the oncoming lane.
