OL,7,FAsked about other evidence, the
OL,8,Fconstable told the court that Mr
OL,9,FPetrov said in his police interview
OL,10,Fthat he is diabetic and that his blood
OL,11,Fsugar was low prior to the collision.
OL,13,F"He stopped to take a chocolate bar
OL,14,Fand felt that he was ok to drive," the
OL,15,Fconstable said.
